comments: Wagner (ORL) is firming up over his left foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick on Gordon (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) contests Anthony's (ORL) reverse attempt and marginal arm contact occurs after the release.
Suggs (ORL) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Banchero (ORL) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) left wrist and front as Jokic elevates for the layup attempt.
Queen (ORL) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Jokic (DEN) after Jokic secures the rebound.
Queen's (ORL) left foot steps out of bounds as he attempts to save the ball along the sideline.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Wagner's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen.
Banchero (ORL) and Queen (ORL) each bring an arm forward to contest the dunk attempt and marginal contact occurs with Gordon's (DEN) right and left arm, respectively, as Gordon finishes at the rim.
Wagner (ORL) is firming up over his left foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick on Gordon (DEN).
Gordon's (DEN) right forearm brushes Banchero's (ORL) side, and marginal contact occurs at the end of Banchero's drive and after his gather.
Banchero (ORL) and Wagner (ORL) each move forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Murray's (DEN) front/side after Murray secures the rebound.
Banchero (ORL) initiates contact across Murray's (DEN) left arm, subsequently allowing Banchero to then make contact with the ball as Murray dribbles in transition.
Gordon (DEN) initiates body and arm contact with Banchero (ORL), affecting Banchero's driving shot attempt.
Suggs (ORL) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Murray (DEN) as Murray dribbles in the backcourt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Suggs' (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Harris (ORL) aligns to move alongside Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs with Caldwell-Pope's side as he makes the pass at the end of the drive.
Murray (DEN) is turning when marginal body contact occurs with Wagner (ORL) after Wagner releases the pass.
Jokic (DEN) initiates contact across Banchero's (ORL) right arm and affects his dunk attempt.
Wagner (ORL) moves somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with Murray's (DEN) side after Murray receives the pass at the top of the perimeter.

Queen (ORL) avoids making contact with Murray (DEN) and legally contests Murray's shot attempt. Wagner (ORL) jumps ahead of and is turning away from Murray, and would avoid Murray if he did not slightly extend his right leg forward to initiate marginal body contact during the shot attempt.
